## When to use this component
Use the password component when you need users to create or enter secret information they are likely to want hidden while they enter it.

## How to use this component
The `<input>` and `<label>` is separated by a [checkbox component](/components/checkbox) with classes `js-password-toggle-wrap` and `checkbox--toggle` on the wrapping `<div>` and `js-password-toggle` on the `<input>`.

